          C
          
            0
          
        
      
    
    {\displaystyle C_{1}\oplus C_{0}}
  ; the source morphism is just the projection onto 
  
    
      
        
          C
          
            0
          
        
      
    
    {\displaystyle C_{0}}
   while the target morphism is the addition of projection onto 
  
    
      
        
          C
          
            1
          
        
      
    
